tourBios.otherInfo: Winner 1984 Magnolia Classic...Finished two strokes behind winner Dillard Pruitt at 1991 Chattanooga Classic...Previously caddied for Jesper Parnevik on the PGA TOUR.

tourBios.carHigh: 2012: Was the 36-hole leader at the U.S. Senior Open and he eventually finished T9, his best Champions Tour finish. Earned his way into the event by being the medalist at the sectional qualifier in Paramus, N.J.
